query:
SELECT 
  b.id,
  b.status,
  b.startDate,
  b.ownerAmount,
  sc.name as centreName
FROM bookings b
JOIN sites s ON b.siteId = s.id
JOIN shopping_centres sc ON s.centreId = sc.id
WHERE b.status = 'confirmed'
  AND b.startDate >= '2025-07-01'
  AND b.startDate <= '2026-06-30'
ORDER BY b.startDate
LIMIT 30;
